Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.20,0:00:03.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,七宮？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.88,0:00:06.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這樣…不行的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.71,0:00:09.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不行的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.82,0:00:15.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒有戀愛經驗的我
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.63,0:00:17.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對於這種事情一直很遲鈍
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.30,0:00:19.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,七宮
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.91,0:00:24.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就算是這樣的我 當看到她流下眼淚之時也發覺了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.39,0:00:27.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,七宮到底是在和什麼做鬥爭
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.22,0:00:29.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為什麼問我那種問題
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.00,0:00:31.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為什麼會想說那樣的話
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.01,0:00:36.52,Comment,NTP,0,0,0,,水魔導師的攻擊變強大了 請求救援
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.89,0:00:38.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,還有她哭泣的原因
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.56,0:00:47.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你在幹什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.12,0:00:51.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,新發現 現在準備開始探索
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.66,0:00:52.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不可以
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.91,0:00:54.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你沒有帶傘吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.58,0:00:56.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是因為樟葉…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.61,0:00:58.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為什麼會和樟葉扯上關係
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.00,0:01:00.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好啦 快進來
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.66,0:01:02.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,身體都變涼了喲
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.82,0:01:06.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,黑暗住民的體溫本來就是這麼…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,OP----
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.20,0:02:54.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我進來了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.10,0:02:56.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我做了點菜粥
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.96,0:02:57.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,稍微吃點吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.49,0:03:03.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,400)\pos(608,318)\3c&H000000&\fs29}Episode XI 蒼月下的…最終決戰
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.49,0:03:03.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,400)\pos(664,288)\3c&H000000&\fs21}Blue moon·Ragnarok
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.53,0:03:03.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,稍微坐起來一點吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.24,0:03:09.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,現實世界出現了歪曲
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.85,0:03:13.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是因為邪王真眼的力量也在減弱…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.09,0:03:14.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.00,0:03:18.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看來燒還是沒退下去
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.01,0:03:21.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今天也給我乖乖在家睡覺哦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.57,0:03:24.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那可不行
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.95,0:03:27.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我說你啊 都已經感冒了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.34,0:03:30.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,昨天還勉強自己想到外面去
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.54,0:03:32.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很快就覺得頭暈了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.27,0:03:35.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,世界要消失了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.27,0:03:35.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(451,438)\fs21}Vanishiment
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.87,0:03:36.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,已經沒事了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.96,0:03:38.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,睡了一晚已經得到完全恢復
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.80,0:03:41.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不行 直到病好為止都不准你出去
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.40,0:03:43.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,話說 你到底是想去哪裡呀
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.64,0:03:45.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這個我不能回答你
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.38,0:03:46.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我之前應該也說過
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.25,0:03:49.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我以闇炎之主的身份提問
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.44,0:03:50.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你到底打算去哪
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.93,0:03:57.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我問完之後也不打算責怪你什麼的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.39,0:03:59.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只是很討厭這種感覺
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.27,0:04:03.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,六花對我有所隱瞞而去其他地方
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.09,0:04:07.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.91,0:04:10.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真相很快就會昭然於天下
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.94,0:04:15.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,主人 為什麼要撇下凸守我
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.53,0:04:17.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,變成這副樣子啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.38,0:04:19.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,de…death
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.02,0:04:20.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她還沒有死啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.27,0:04:21.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,馬上就會好了對吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.14,0:04:23.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果你那麼介意的話
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.17,0:04:25.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我隨時都可以依靠邪王真眼的力量恢復健康
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.08,0:04:26.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只是…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.87,0:04:28.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.20,0:04:35.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,難道必須要服下盛開於邪王崖暗黑壁之巔的黑龍花才能痊癒嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.42,0:04:38.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,別隨意添加設定
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.80,0:04:39.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你站得那麼近小心被傳染啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.10,0:04:41.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,主人 等著我
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.73,0:04:44.02,Comment,NTP,0,0,0,,凸守我一定會…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.83,0:04:43.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,謝謝你們兩位
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.17,0:04:45.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是待得太久也有被傳染的危險
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.96,0:04:47.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.75,0:04:52.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再見 奇美拉
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.61,0:04:54.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要快點恢復哦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.25,0:04:55.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,作業堆了很多了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.92,0:04:58.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你剛剛說出了禁言
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.01,0:04:59.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你說什麼！？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.67,0:05:01.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,忘了作業會皺眉頭哦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.93,0:05:03.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對了 索菲婭呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.07,0:05:09.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我好幾次想通過電子音信識別信號與她聯絡
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.37,0:05:11.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是卻從來沒得到她的回應
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.65,0:05:13.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是嗎 到底怎麼回事呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.18,0:05:16.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那傢伙好像說她很忙
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.29,0:05:17.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很容易就能看出來啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.69,0:05:22.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,七宮說了要開始戰爭的時候
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.83,0:05:25.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我就猜到大概就會發展到這個地步
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.87,0:05:27.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那麼丹谷生你是發現了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.13,0:05:29.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一眼就發現了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.21,0:05:33.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那個孩子眼裡就只有你一個人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.35,0:05:36.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,其實是十花姐告訴我們的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.52,0:05:38.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那這之後你打算怎麼做
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.67,0:05:39.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,打算是指…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.89,0:05:41.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不可能對那個孩子坐視不管吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.97,0:05:44.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她那麼喜歡你啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.65,0:05:46.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就算你突然這麼跟我說
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.95,0:05:48.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也不知道該怎麼做啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.84,0:05:50.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她甚至也從來沒有跟我說過那種事
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.82,0:05:53.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你怎麼突然變得這麼正經了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.84,0:05:55.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我只是在說實話
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.79,0:05:56.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼做才好呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.90,0:05:57.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.65,0:05:59.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,女生應該比較更瞭解戀愛這回事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.98,0:06:02.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我怎麼會知道啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.59,0:06:05.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你在迴避嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.67,0:06:07.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒有刻意迴避哦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.84,0:06:09.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那你就別插手這件事了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.63,0:06:12.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,六花那個時候也是 總是發生什麼立刻就…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.44,0:06:15.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是因為看富樫你們很煩惱
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.08,0:06:16.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,才來幫助你們的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.80,0:06:19.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我可沒記得有拜託過你
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.84,0:06:20.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我懂了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.06,0:06:22.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那就隨你便吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.57,0:06:23.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,茴香學姐 我們走
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.49,0:06:38.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你在幹什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.46,0:06:39.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.65,0:06:41.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒什麼的話你不要把人撞倒啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.45,0:06:43.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒什麼但是什麼都有！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.91,0:06:43.59,Comment,NTP,0,0,0,,你是凸守嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.45,0:06:50.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,七宮？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.57,0:06:52.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,勇者
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.36,0:06:53.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她在做什麼呀
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.21,0:06:59.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,成功歸來
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.98,0:07:01.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你到底在做什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.32,0:07:02.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一不小心你就死了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.59,0:07:07.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果要戰勝內在的自己 就需要波紋和魔法能量
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.05,0:07:09.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,原來是這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.28,0:07:10.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要這麼輕易贊同啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.83,0:07:13.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,多虧這個這次我也成功打敗敵人
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.83,0:07:15.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,取得了最終勝利喲
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.58,0:07:20.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,從今往後 我就是魔法魔王少女改+α外傳了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.94,0:07:24.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼有種續篇繼續爛牌遊戲的感覺
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.44,0:07:28.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因此以前的事以後已經全部被我遺棄到了無知的盡頭
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.29,0:07:30.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,統統消失吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.41,0:07:35.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,七宮 這樣真的可以嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.08,0:07:39.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這樣就好了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.41,0:07:42.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那就好
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.15,0:07:46.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是天使的反應
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.64,0:07:50.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,富樫同學
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.72,0:07:51.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼了？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.59,0:07:53.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你該不會把她剛才的話當真
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.77,0:07:57.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想著「太好了 好像她沒事」之類的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.43,0:07:58.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,難道不是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.31,0:08:01.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你在做什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.15,0:08:03.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼可能 她只是在逞強
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.74,0:08:05.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那種事怎麼可能看得出來
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.25,0:08:06.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,當然看得出來
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.41,0:08:09.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我和七宮的交情也不是這一兩天的事情了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.08,0:08:12.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那…你要我到底怎麼辦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.95,0:08:13.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.04,0:08:16.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,俗話說戀情如夢嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.73,0:08:17.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果是夢的話
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.88,0:08:20.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,隨著時間的流逝應該會慢慢地醒過來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.98,0:08:24.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果要強行叫醒她的話 反而會讓她覺得痛苦吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.73,0:08:29.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,茴香學姐
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.49,0:08:32.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你要去哪裡
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.58,0:08:34.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒什麼 這不關你事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.65,0:08:37.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.58,0:08:39.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,其實小森大人她最喜歡你們了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.54,0:08:46.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喜歡小六花 小凸守還有富樫同學 小七宮
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.79,0:08:49.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她最喜歡中二病了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.73,0:08:52.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我都覺得羨慕她呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.80,0:08:55.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果我是中二病就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.15,0:08:55.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,學姐你那麼想？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.29,0:08:59.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那樣的話 我就能和大家分享同一種感覺了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.09,0:09:03.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是也不是那麼容易就能變成中二病的對吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.53,0:09:06.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,從你開始憧憬的那一刻開始
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.92,0:09:08.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你就是一名堂堂正正的中二病了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.68,0:09:09.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.93,0:09:12.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,茴香學姐你不是第二代邪王真眼嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.45,0:09:30.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,森夏
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.45,0:09:30.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(424,438)\fs21}Mori Summer
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.77,0:09:33.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,索菲亞 你好像處於迷茫之中
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.18,0:09:35.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你怎麼了 這麼突然
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.71,0:09:38.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,難道你已經取回你的記憶了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.59,0:09:40.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你要吃藥草嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.98,0:09:42.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,才不要啦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.70,0:09:44.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只是想著這樣比較容易對你傳達我的想法
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.04,0:09:47.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,才特地換衣服過來的嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.28,0:09:48.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這裙子可是很緊的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.09,0:09:52.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,索菲亞啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.64,0:09:55.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我有箴言相贈
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.67,0:09:58.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這是魔法師 森夏的箴言
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.67,0:09:58.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(457,438)\fs21}Mori Summer
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.89,0:10:02.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,森夏以前曾與冒名之人戰鬥
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.89,0:10:02.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(275,438)\fs21}Mori Summer
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.12,0:10:03.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,並且對他們降下了懲罰
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.04,0:10:05.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那時 我明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.53,0:10:11.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如何面對自己體內的另一個自己並與之對戰的方法
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.19,0:10:13.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,另一個…自己？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.31,0:10:18.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的 為了瞭解自己 應該將目光轉向外面
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.22,0:10:22.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就像我經由與冒牌貨的對戰 得以瞭解自己一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.97,0:10:25.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,索菲亞你也有不得不戰的對手才對
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.47,0:10:28.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,請去尋找那個對手吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.76,0:10:29.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,森夏
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.76,0:10:29.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(424,438)\fs21}Mori Summer
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.94,0:10:32.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那時 你的前途將會一片光明吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.50,0:10:34.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,謝謝你
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.82,0:10:39.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是麻煩啊 你懂了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.36,0:10:40.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,森夏
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.36,0:10:40.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(424,438)\fs21}Mori Summer
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.53,0:10:43.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,謝謝你 我幫你補充魔力
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.33,0:10:45.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你好近啊 住手
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.00,0:10:46.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.42,0:10:48.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雷霆戰錘使
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.42,0:10:48.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(424,438)\fs21}Mjolnir Hammer
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.76,0:10:50.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快點過來
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.26,0:10:56.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你不僅對闇炎之主出手 還把魔爪伸向了冒牌森大人嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.42,0:10:58.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,無法原諒
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.25,0:11:05.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,身體怎麼樣
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.93,0:11:08.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,樟葉 月亮出來了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.53,0:11:09.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是漂亮的滿月哦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.20,0:11:11.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,據說今晚是蒼月呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.25,0:11:13.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,蒼藍…之月
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.72,0:11:18.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,七宮喜歡我 但是我對六花…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.59,0:11:21.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,搞不懂 太複雜了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.28,0:11:22.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到底該怎麼辦…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.54,0:11:26.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,七宮…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.16,0:11:29.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,勇者…不
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.82,0:11:31.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,闇炎之主
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.85,0:11:34.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你要看看我的魔法嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.44,0:11:45.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,七宮…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.53,0:11:46.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雖然我尋找了很久
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.58,0:11:50.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但我的對手果然只有勇者你一個
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.30,0:11:52.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只能這樣做一個了結
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.45,0:11:54.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.81,0:11:56.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這是戰爭！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.26,0:11:58.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是 你…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.30,0:11:58.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我要上了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.50,0:12:00.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,魔王認證
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.37,0:12:02.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.46,0:12:03.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,七宮…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.87,0:12:06.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哥哥 六花不見了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.82,0:12:09.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,剛才稍微不注意她就…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.26,0:12:10.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那傢伙…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.56,0:12:12.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼辦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.04,0:12:13.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,七宮
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.38,0:12:19.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今晚有蒼月對吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.15,0:12:21.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大概 她已經注意到了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.32,0:12:24.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今晚是蒼藍之月的夜晚
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.36,0:12:26.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,蒼藍之月？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.93,0:12:29.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你真的記不得了嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.48,0:12:36.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是這個嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.37,0:12:40.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,暗炎龍？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.70,0:12:43.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,勇者你曾經說過
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.15,0:12:47.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沉睡在自己體內的暗炎龍又會甦醒
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.09,0:12:49.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你也希望它能被人喚醒
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.24,0:12:53.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,來自幾經風霜的過去
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.80,0:12:56.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,未來永恆不變的絕對契約者
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.63,0:13:01.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,即使超越時間 超越次元 前往平行世界的彼方
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.15,0:13:03.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也意欲繼續契約
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.77,0:13:07.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,以其絕對的力量出現在我面前的存在啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.44,0:13:12.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,吾錯誤地降生到這個混沌不堪的世界
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.20,0:13:16.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因其強大的封印之力以及其篡改記憶的嘗試
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.89,0:13:19.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,自己真正的記憶正在逐漸被剝奪
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.27,0:13:23.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,吾恐怕在不久的將來會化歸虛無
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.65,0:13:27.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以吾托付給汝 遙遠的汝
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.78,0:13:29.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,將寄宿我體內的暗炎龍…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.74,0:13:32.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,讓它的身姿在這個世界現身的力量…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.92,0:13:37.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,吞噬 改變 重鑄這個錯誤的世界的力量…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.98,0:13:41.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,復活暗炎龍的鑰匙有三個
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.21,0:13:46.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,斯庫爾德
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.29,0:13:49.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,薇兒丹蒂
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.98,0:13:52.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,兀兒德
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.21,0:13:52.60,Comment,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an7\fs21}註：北歐神話中的諾恩三女神，是北歐神話中的命運女神。
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.55,0:13:55.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果是我絕對的契約者
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.67,0:13:58.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是有著與我共命運的力量之人
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.41,0:14:01.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,收集這三個鑰匙應該不在話下
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.76,0:14:04.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,吾之永遠契約者啊 我將會等待那個時刻的到來
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.97,0:14:06.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,暫時步入沉睡
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.19,0:14:08.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在終將到來的蒼藍之月夜
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.32,0:14:11.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,希望你能將那力量交給我
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.55,0:14:17.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這裡就是…隱藏的地方？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.32,0:14:21.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雖然記得不太清楚 大概就在這附近
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.05,0:14:27.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這是…有人挖的…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.92,0:14:32.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這是？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.11,0:14:34.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這是邪王真眼放在這裡的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.56,0:14:36.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大概
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.62,0:14:38.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大概是找過這裡的標記
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.96,0:14:40.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,該不會…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.11,0:14:42.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.68,0:14:44.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也找過
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.80,0:14:47.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼都找不到兀兒德
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.38,0:14:49.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是送往過去的鑰匙
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.28,0:14:53.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為了將鑰匙送往過去 只能使用平行世界了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.47,0:14:57.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那張筆記裡提到的平行世界的入口
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.46,0:14:59.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就在第十四個鐵塔所指向的陰影之下
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.37,0:15:03.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是我不知道那是從哪裡開始數的第十四個
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.32,0:15:05.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為了找到那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.61,0:15:07.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她就這樣一點一滴地徹查
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.49,0:15:17.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抱歉…但是
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.10,0:15:19.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,「真相很快就會昭然於天下」
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.50,0:15:22.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那傢伙…一直為了這個
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.32,0:15:26.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你想起來了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.18,0:15:29.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,模模糊糊地
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.82,0:15:31.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這附近的風景我有印象
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.62,0:15:36.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在這邊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.32,0:15:41.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,六花…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.28,0:15:45.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你 無論何時都那麼認真地去中二
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.46,0:15:48.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,無論何時都那麼認真地去戀愛
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.29,0:15:51.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一直都在為我著想
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.34,0:15:55.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,六花 六花 六花
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.11,0:15:57.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,勇者…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.21,0:16:07.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,六花！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.27,0:16:10.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,勇太？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.82,0:16:14.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你…在做什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.65,0:16:16.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,勇太 這個就是…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.34,0:16:26.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,兀兒德？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.32,0:16:26.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.33,0:16:30.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你明明感冒了 還來找這種東西嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.88,0:16:32.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要是惡化了怎麼辦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.60,0:16:35.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因為必須由絕對的契約者
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.59,0:16:38.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,永遠的契約者來喚醒…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.46,0:16:39.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就算如此…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.98,0:16:42.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是勇太的永遠的契約者
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.00,0:16:44.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以 必須找出來才行
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.15,0:16:46.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,找出來 將它作為證明…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.31,0:16:52.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,勇太？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.09,0:16:54.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你在做什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.65,0:16:56.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那種事不用做也沒關係的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.16,0:16:57.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因為…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.45,0:17:02.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我明明是契約者 卻連一把鑰匙都沒有
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.21,0:17:04.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是索菲亞卻…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.74,0:17:05.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.77,0:17:08.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好痛苦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.13,0:17:12.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,勇太…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.27,0:17:17.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,勇太是我的契約者？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.33,0:17:21.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊 是你絕對的契約者
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.97,0:17:34.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我在國中二年級的時候骨折了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.09,0:17:36.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,居然把它塞進那時的石膏裡面
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.39,0:17:40.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那時的我 居然還做了這麼麻煩的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.29,0:17:42.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拿去
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.59,0:17:52.93,Comment,NTP,0,0,0,,水與柱
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.69,0:17:53.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,厲害
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.11,0:17:56.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,僅此而已的話 誰都看不懂吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.70,0:17:59.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在金屬上面刻字很麻煩 所以中途就放棄了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.33,0:18:06.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明明是很多年前放在這兒的東西 居然還在這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.28,0:18:10.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明明只是塊石頭而已
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.32,0:18:14.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那就是喚醒暗炎龍的魔石…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.24,0:18:15.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,姑且算是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.78,0:18:16.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,蒼藍之月…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.12,0:18:18.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那時我查過
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.07,0:18:20.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今天就是蒼月
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.32,0:18:22.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,六花…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.40,0:18:25.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不 拜託你了 邪王真眼
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.16,0:18:31.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我永遠的契約者啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.36,0:18:33.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,爆裂吧 現實
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.01,0:18:35.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,綻開吧 神經突觸
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.92,0:18:41.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Vanishment this world！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.56,0:19:05.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好厲害
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.05,0:19:07.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,勇者
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.12,0:19:09.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不 格爾松尼盎斯
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.12,0:19:09.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(441,438)\fs21}Ghelzonianses
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.79,0:19:12.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這是戰爭 讓我與你的暗炎龍一決勝負
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.64,0:19:13.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,用你的全力
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.85,0:19:14.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.78,0:19:15.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我終於明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.98,0:19:19.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我應當與之一戰的對手 不可不戰的敵人
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.37,0:19:24.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那就是與勇者齊思 共求 同棄的暗炎龍
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.80,0:19:26.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那就是我不可不戰的敵人
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.21,0:19:29.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是我必須決出勝負的對手
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.70,0:19:33.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,七宮…我明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.29,0:19:35.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是格爾松尼盎斯
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.29,0:19:35.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(451,438)\fs21}Ghelzonianses
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.94,0:19:38.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,破壞並重鑄世界一切的人
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.26,0:19:42.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,魔法魔王少女 期望未來永恆獲得魔法的人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.42,0:19:44.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就讓吾之暗炎龍的力量…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.30,0:19:49.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,深深地烙印進你的雙目中吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.53,0:19:51.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如我所願
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.23,0:20:15.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,暗炎龍根本不可能存在
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.54,0:20:20.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,當然更不可能被看見
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.33,0:20:22.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.27,0:20:35.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這…這是什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.40,0:20:37.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.89,0:20:43.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那之後 六花的感冒復發倒床不起
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.41,0:20:47.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,勇太 我要回溯時空
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.59,0:20:49.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,讓現在變成7月8日…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.21,0:20:50.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不可能
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.29,0:20:54.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,背負著崩潰狀態的作業 迎來了暑假的結束
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.57,0:20:57.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是那樣的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.18,0:20:59.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,作業寫不完啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.66,0:21:01.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,夢葉長大了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.71,0:21:02.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,夢葉也要說話
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.36,0:21:07.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,結果 我還是一次都沒去過她們希望我過去的雅加達
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.60,0:21:09.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然後…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.36,0:21:12.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你的作業沒事嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.96,0:21:16.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對於新生的索菲亞來說這不是什麼問題
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.02,0:21:19.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,七宮在結束了與暗炎龍的戰鬥之後
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.96,0:21:22.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,完成了向新的七宮的進化
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.56,0:21:25.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你啊 到底什麼地方改變了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.47,0:21:29.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是不會變的 未來永遠我都是魔法魔王少女
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.65,0:21:33.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以吾以不變之名 將郁集的東西破壞掉
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.48,0:21:37.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為了保持不變從而需要參加使自己變得強大的戰鬥
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.33,0:21:40.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.26,0:21:42.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是說不定…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.66,0:21:44.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那就是連關定則嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.71,0:21:49.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是吧 那就是連關定則哦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.77,0:21:52.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今天你也要找天使嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.37,0:21:55.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那個…勇者
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.13,0:22:01.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拜拜
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,【ED】
