Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.68,0:23:11.26,ED1,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be6\blur8\bord1\3c&HFF35FF&}愚者は月影に虚妄を抱く
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.44,0:23:14.07,ED1,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be6\blur8\bord1\3c&HFF35FF&}現実世界-ゲーム-が僕らを
